463
00:31:41,365 --> 00:31:43,038
Vãi thật.

464
00:31:46,971 --> 00:31:48,245
...

465
00:31:49,874 --> 00:31:50,978
Abraham.

466
00:31:53,711 --> 00:31:57,716
